  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink292-kilavi">piṉmuṟai ākkiya perumporuḷ vatuvai muṭittavaḷai yillattuk koṇṭu pukuntuḻit talaimakaḷ uvantu colliyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> 
          What the heroine said happily when she entered, having brought [with her] the one who had completed the marriage of great value, which is subsequent in order [to her own marriage].                
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink292">
<l>mayilka ḷālap peruntē ṉimirat</l>
<l>taṇmaḻai taḻīiya māmalai nāṭa</l>
<l>niṉṉiṉuñ ciṟantaṉa ḷemakkē nīnayantu</l>
<l>naṉmaṉai yaruṅkaṭi yayara</l>
<l>vennalañ ciṟappayā miṉippeṟ ṟōḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>O man from the land on the great mountain,</l>
        <l>embraced by cool clouds,</l>
        <l>as peacocks dance and great bees hum—</l>
        <l rend="space">she has become more excellent than you to us—</l>
        <l>she, obtained by us for our beauty to increase,</l>
        <l>as you, desiring [her],</l>
        <l>undertook the difficult protection of this good house.</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
